        <mxCell id="s8b" value="&lt;b&gt;⚠ Auth Failed&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;i&gt;401 - Token expired&lt;br&gt;Log warning&lt;/i&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontFamily=Segoe UI;fontSize=12;" vertex="1" parent="1">
